function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	-- Start Cutscene
	CampaignForcedPartyGatherPlayIGC(convRTC, idActorPlayer)
	
	-- Set Vigo to kneeling
	Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(actorMonkOutside)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorMonkOutside, animsetKneel)
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(actorMonkOutside, actorIosefPostChapelLoc)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorMonkOutside, actorIosefPostChapelLoc)
	bMonkWasTeleported = true


end

function Start()
	-- Conditioned to only fire if the player is not continuing directly from
	-- previous quest.
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorVaniCorpse)
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(actorMonkOutside, actorChapelLoc)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorMonkOutside)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorMonkOutside, actorChapelLoc)
	
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorMonkOutside)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(actorMonkOutside, "NPC_Frac_Prologue_Monk2")
	
end

function Start()

	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActors()
	
	-- Check if any players have the Chapel key already
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		if Hydra.ActorHasItemByName(Player, itemChapelKey) then
			Hydra.EventSend("HaveChapelKey")
			break
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActor)	
	if bMonkWasTeleported == false then
		Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorMonkOutside, animsetKneel)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorMonkOutside, "NPC_Idle_Kneel_Prayer")
		Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(actorMonkOutside, "NPC_Frac_Prologue_Monk2")
	end
end
